        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="m-3 mb-mb-0 mx-auto text-center">Specbuilder Project 1: Safe Driving Campaign</h2>
            <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between mb-5 mt-5">
                <div class="w-75 mx-auto h-30">
                    <img src="img/Specbuilder_01-Safe-driving.jpg" class="img-fluid card card-cover  overflow-hidden p-0 m-0 text-white bg-dark rounded-5 shadow-lg" alt="" />
                </div>
                <div class="text-center mt-3 p-md-5 col-md-9 mx-auto">
                    <p>
                        Through this ad I wish to promote safe driving and
                        responsible drinking. It is shown using the beer pong
                        game. Beer pong is a drinking game which is often
                        played by two teams with two or more members in each
                        team.Safe driving is important. It is important to
                        oneself and to others. Alcohol dampens the drinker’s
                        alertness and cognitive functions.  a driver is 11
                        times more likely than the non-drinking driver to be
                        involved in a crash.Take the assistance of others when
                        drunk. Always drink responsibly and never play both the
                        games of drink and drive. Choose either.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

