    <section id="sb3" class="p-2 bg-dark text-light">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="m-3 mb-mb-0 mx-auto text-center">Specbuilder Project 3: Lacoste Shirt</h2>
            <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between mb-5 mt-5">
                <div class="w-75 mx-auto h-30">
                    <img src="img/Specbuilder_03-Lacoste.jpg" class="img-fluid card card-cover  overflow-hidden p-0 m-0 text-white bg-dark rounded-5 shadow-lg" alt="" />
                </div>
                <div class="text-center mt-3 p-md-5 col-md-9  mx-auto">
                    <p>
                        Lacoste is a brand founded by Rene Lacoste, a legendary
                        tennis player. Lacoste started an unexpected protest of
                        dressing norms in the 1930s tennis circuit. He soon
                        built a brand that would resonate with people globally.
                        The brand is best known for their Polos pinned with the
                        memorable crocodile. In this ad, I have envisioned and
                        visualised the brand’s boldness in a sweatshirt. Which
                        is a representation of the tenacity carried by Lacoste
                        himself on the court, which is also representative of a
                        crocodile’s ability.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

